OL,3,CParents of SEND children 'quit jobs'
OL,4,Cand take out loans to care for children
OL,6,FOne in three parents of children with
OL,7,Fspecial educational needs is now
OL,8,Freporting they're having to quit their
OL,9,Fjobs - almost as many having to rely
OL,10,Fon benefits.
OL,12,FLong-delayed changes to SEND education
OL,13,Fsoon expected - 60,000 new specialist
OL,14,Fplaces at mainstream schools and a
OL,15,F#3.7bn overhaul already announced.
