OL,3,CParents of SEND children 'quit jobs'
OL,4,Cand take out loans to care for children
OL,6,FA survey shared exclusively with ITV
OL,7,FNews by the Disabled Children's
OL,8,FPartnership found that 34% of parents
OL,9,Fwith SEND children have had to reduce
OL,10,Ftheir working hours and around a
OL,11,Fquarter (22%) have had to change jobs
OL,12,Fand 31% of families have to rely on
OL,13,Fbenefits due to the financial pressure
OL,14,Fof supporting a child with SEND.
OL,16,FSara Donelly's teaching career has
OL,17,Fgone from being in charge of a school
OL,18,Fof hundreds to a class of one because
OL,19,Fshe says support for her daughter
OL,20,Fwasn't there.
