OL,6,FThe Department for Education told us:
OL,7,F"For too long, families have been
OL,8,Fforced to fight for support that
OL,9,Fshould be routinely available... Our
OL,10,Freforms will create a better system
OL,11,Ffor all - where support is delivered
OL,12,Fearlier and closer to home."
OL,14,FA placement at a specialist school for
OL,15,FAva set to begin in April.
